reviewText: Great old movies where the hero always win. Loved them.
I love John Wayne cowboys, especially the older ones.  These are great.  I really like the Three Mesquiteers movies!
If you love John Wayne then these movies should be in your library.
Since I am a Jjhn Wayne fan, I like almost anything he has done as I did this one also.
It is fun to watch the old John Wayne westerns that would not normally ever be shown anywhere in these times.
Typical +/- hour long movies of the time and the genre. John Wayne does his basic acting job not brilliant like in his later movies but every one must hone their craft.
